FBIS4-23784 "drafr116bb_94006" FBIS-AFR-94-116 Daily Report 15 Jun 1994 INTER-AFRICAN AFFAIRS Nigeria, S. Africa Join Conflict Resolution Bureau Nigeria, S. Africa Join Conflict Resolution Bureau AB1506204694 Lagos Radio Nigeria Network in English 1800 GMT 15 Jun 94 AB1506204694 Lagos Radio Nigeria Network English BFN [Excerpt] Nigeria has been admitted into the OAU Bureau on Conflict Resolution. Nigeria's admission is contained in a communique issued at the end of the 30th summit of the organization, which ended today in Tunis, Tunisia. State House correspondent, Orji Ogbonia Orji, reports that seven other African countries, including South Africa, are also members. [passage omitted]
